{"tid":1976940,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五警申終極上訴遭駁回 終審判詞：上訴方誤解裁決理由 再爭議證供呈堂門檻將淪學術討論","createTime":"2020-04-17T14:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:00:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aec35a303b35c975c5533a8803e2c6cdb27c188d","tid":1976940,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"2014 年佔領運動期間，7 名警察執勤時涉在金鐘添馬公園將社工曾健超抬到「暗角」圍毆，2017 年被裁定襲擊致造成身體傷害罪成，各被判監兩年。7 人其後就定罪及刑期上訴，上訴庭裁定其中 2 人上訴得直，其餘 5 人定罪上訴遭駁回，本月初向終審法院再申請上訴許可遭拒。終審法院今（17 日）頒下判詞解釋，原審法官依賴處理涉案片段的證人供詞，已可證明影片屬實及呈堂，上訴方誤解原審法官採納的標準，認為再於終院爭議證供呈堂門檻，只會淪為學術討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BA%94%E8%AD%A6%E7%94%B3%E7%B5%82%E6%A5%B5%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E-%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E5%88%A4%E8%A9%9E-%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4%E6%96%B9%E8%AA%A4%E8%A7%A3%E8%A3%81%E6%B1%BA%E7%90%86%E7%94%B1-%E5%86%8D%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%91%88%E5%A0%82%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%E5%B0%87%E6%B7%AA%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%2588%25A4%25E8%25A9%259E-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E7%2590%2586%25E7%2594%25B1-%25E5%2586%258D%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25AD%2589%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU9wxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=4cedd9ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BA%2594%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%2594%25B3%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%25A7%2581%25E5%259B%259E-%25E7%25B5%2582